                    },
                    "body": "Please evaluate and categorize as necessary.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=wil",
                        "name": "wil",
                        "displayName": "Wil Sinclair",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-03-31T15:01:47.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-03-31T15:01:47.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/22929",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=miallen",
                        "name": "miallen",
                        "displayName": "Michael B Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Fixed in r10171.\n\nNote that Zend_Ldap has always supported anonymous binds. However, to do so required supplying a username and a null password which is strange to say the least.\n\nTherefore, the semantics of the Zend_Ldap::bind() method has been changed slightly so that if the username is null (or not supplied) this is interpreted as a desire to bind with the default credentials or anonymously if no default credentials are supplied. So to bind anonymously, you simply do not supply default credentials and do not supply parameters to bind (or supply a null username).\n\nNote that it is currently not possible to perform an anonymous bind if default credentials have been supplied. We could check to see if parameters were supplied to Zend_Ldap::bind() and perform or not perform the bind anonymously based on that. But that could be awkward and it's not clear that we need this feature.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=miallen",
                        "name": "miallen",
                        "displayName": "Michael B Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2008-07-17T22:09:39.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2008-07-17T22:09:39.000+0000"
                },
